### update customers mapping
PUT http://localhost:9200/customers/_mapping
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "date_detection": true,
    "dynamic_date_formats": [
        "yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss",
        "yyyy-MM-dd",
        "yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss",
        "yyyy/MM/dd"
    ],
    "numeric_detection": true
}

